Attachments
precis:
Authority for the Minister of the Environment to enter into an AGREEMENT
with the Province of Quebec, Hydro-Québec, Alcan and the Société de
protection des forêts contre le feu for the purpose of carrying out
activities in support of meteorological observation in Quebec.
